strings: <tag_voice_0x01001C25><se_low>Morrie: When we are coming back here, <nickname>, I have the business to attend to. My pit does not run on itself, ay!
<voice_0x01001C2A><se_low>Morrie: I must bring the dead monster in the teams back to the life, and all these things.
<voice_0x01001C2B><se_low>Morrie: So, scusi, but I must <endash> How do you say? <endash> make myself scared for a while!
<voice_0x01001C2C><se_low>Morrie: I see you in the arena, ay?
